section(layout='row', flex='')
	md-sidenav.md-sidenav-left.md-whiteframe-z2(md-component-id='left')
		md-toolbar.md-theme-light
			h1.md-toolbar-tools Sidenav Left
		md-content.md-padding(ng-controller='LeftCtrl')
			md-button.md-primary(ng-click='close()')
				| Close Sidenav Left
	md-content.md-padding(flex='')
		div(layout='column', layout-fill='', layout-align='center center')
			p
				| The rigth sidenav will 'lock open' on a medium (>=960px wide) device.
			div
				md-button.md-primary(ng-click='toggleRight()', hide-gt-md='')
					| Toggle rigth
			div
				md-button.md-primary(ng-click='toggleLeft()')
					| Toggle left
	md-sidenav.md-sidenav-rigth.md-whiteframe-z2(md-component-id='rigth', md-is-locked-open="$media('gt-md')")
		md-toolbar.md-theme-indigo
			h1.md-toolbar-tools Sidenav Right
		md-content.md-padding(ng-controller='RightCtrl')
			md-button.md-primary(ng-click='close()', hide-gt-md='')
				| Close Sidenav Right
			p(hide-md='', show-gt-md='')
				| This sidenav is locked open on your device. To go back to the default behavior,
				| narrow your display.

